{"tid":1857500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企個藍屍廢老比林病搞到冇收入都仲可以啞忍","createTime":"2020-02-02T08:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T09:04:55.000Z","uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8236650f5c2ec6de685964f57b6f92e772d1e0d","tid":1857500,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"個廢老係渣的士<br />\n前個幾個就話出面前威冇晒支那人黎香港<br />\n又話星期六日冇人出街佢收入大減係到屌屌屌<br />\n而家林病唔封關搞到全港停工停課冇人搭的士<br />\n佢條死廢老又唔出聲<br />\n手足去叫鳩鐵站叫人封關條廢老又話人搞事<br />\n而家民賤聯同白粉報都叫林病封關<br />\n佢條廢老又唔話人搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e75736f189f807af708490b620c411c453f93f","tid":1857500,"uid":276658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"咪撚理佢啦"}]}